{"tid":1733231,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"紅隧被封 朝朝谷爆紅底西隧","createTime":"2019-11-18T05:11:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T05:11:54.000Z","uid":295505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2de767e6d1dc8aeb6b9f874c4caf7585200686b8","tid":1733231,"uid":295505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:11:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%80%E6%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E9%9A%A7%E9%81%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25BA%2595%25E9%259A%25A7%25E9%2581%2593&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2RjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=ce6f89cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%80%E6%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E9%9A%A7%E9%81%93</a><br />\n<br />\n現時西隧公司的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最大單一股東為港通控股有限公司</span></strong></span>，持有50%西隧公司股份。其他股東為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中信股份</span></strong></span>（舊名：中信泰富）及嘉里建設，並透過聯營公司分別持有35%及15%西隧公司的權益[6]。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B8%AF%E9%80%9A%E6%8E%A7%E8%82%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2580%259A%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%2582%25A1&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2RjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=63b931b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B8%AF%E9%80%9A%E6%8E%A7%E8%82%A1</a><br />\n而港通之控股股東為渝太地產集團有限公司(港交所：0075)。<br />\n<br />\n港通同渝太主席都係....<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BC%B5%E6%9D%BE%E6%A9%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E6%259D%25BE%25E6%25A9%258B&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2RjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=07cf8575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BC%B5%E6%9D%BE%E6%A9%8B</a><br />\n張松橋 （1964年－），籍貫重慶，重慶商人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">從事房地產開發，有「重慶李嘉誠」及「最富有的重慶人」之稱</span></strong></span>。他是四家香港上市公司的主席。"}]}